content:
Add the Knowledge Article Component to Enhanced LWR Knowledge Pages

To show the right content to your users and help them self-serve with published knowledge articles, add the Knowledge Article component to your enhanced LWR Knowledge page.

Before you add:

* Make sure Knowledge is enabled.
* Create an enhanced LWR site.
* Publish a knowledge article visible to site users.
* Enable guest user access in site Administration workspace.

In Setup:

* Enter Digital Experiences and select Sites.
* Find your enhanced LWR site, go to Builder.
* Go to the Knowledge Detail page.
* Drag and drop the Knowledge Article component to your layout.

Configure content display and publish changes.
title: Adding Knowledge Article Component to Enhanced LWR
